{"tid":2058722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄去信全港校長：學生或教師參與罷課應受懲處","createTime":"2020-06-10T11:29:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T12:54:54.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"88a1a7300106f1ae81b5da0ad1e9ef5a79248a15","tid":2058722,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:29:01.000Z","msg":"教育局長楊潤雄去信全港中小學校長，指近日有團體發起反對港區國安法的網上聯署，故意誤導和煽動學生參與所謂「罷工罷課公投」，政府予以強烈譴責，批評有關活動是以學生的利益和前途作為籌碼，強調學校不應任由學生參加，更不應容許罷課，如果發現有學生組織或慫恿同學參加違法活動、罷課或校內政治活動，應該立即勸止，如屢勸不改，就要按校本訓育輔導和懲處機制處理。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄又指，教師不可以放事假參與罷課，如果參與，將是疏忽職守，將政治帶入校園，向學生示範以違規方式表達訴求，有違專業，校方應採取紀律行動，教育局亦會嚴肅跟進。"},{"pid":"98ef7daa876ae329f5f0507a25b2fcaa4685b8dd","tid":2058722,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:29:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1305201&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1305201%26csid%3D261_341&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=e1ffc377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1305201&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"aba399142a7bb419eb9aa3b5a3b18fd88a80b71a","tid":2058722,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1394c0c13740455a5a7a56e235e533ac16c7872d","tid":2058722,"uid":132810,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"人地罷課關你差事"},{"pid":"8be2857e46536a806fe87a693ad98bb2b4f75953","tid":2058722,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T11:39:03.000Z","msg":"有冇手足去信楊潤雄囝囝的學校，以彼之道，還施彼身，你攪人哋啲仔女，人哋必攪鳩你囝囝。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed1a0a039230cad199dac56db3624f73d4b868c","tid":2058722,"uid":268519,"like":0,"disli